column5: If you are interested I have put the North Western Ontario Socked Lake lists online. They include lake names, GPS stats, year stocked, age of stocked fish and amounts.  North Western Ontario Stocked Lakes.  Roger
very nice of you, stocking lists are a gold mine if you're willing to get out there and find the lakes
